{% comment %}
  Layer 2 content for the DJ earplugs product page.
  Hardcoded influencer quotes, photos and FAQ.
  Referenced by templates/product.dj.json
  Section order in template: 1. Products, 2. Slideshow (scrolling artist images), 3. 3-column feature blocks, 4. This file (testimonials + FAQ)
{% endcomment %}

<style>
  /* DJ page testimonial images — consistent sizing */
  .product-content--dj .testimonial-split__image img,
  .product-dj-content .testimonial-split__image img {
    max-height: 400px;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
</style>

<!-- ── Intro: artist names + hero image ── -->
<div class="product-content__intro">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="product-content__intro-grid">
      <div class="product-content__intro-text" data-reveal>
        <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:clamp(28px,3.5vw,48px);letter-spacing:.04em;margin-bottom:20px;">DJ Earplugs</h2>
        <p>Renowned artists such as <em>Franky Rizardo</em>, <em>Paco Osuna</em>, <em>Danny Avila</em>, <em>ANOTR</em>, <em>Stephan Bodzin</em>, <em>Luuk van Dijk</em>, <em>Mason Collective</em>, <em>Toman</em>, <em>Wade</em>, <em>Joey Daniel</em> and many more have enthusiastically embraced these innovative earplugs and are reaping the benefits.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:20px;font-style:italic;color:var(--color-text-muted);">&ldquo;I've found Earasers to be the most comfortable and clear-sounding ear protection I've used.&rdquo; — Franky Rizardo</p>
        <p style="margin-top:12px;font-style:italic;color:var(--color-text-muted);">&ldquo;Their perfect fit and superior noise reduction make them my top pick for any performance.&rdquo; — WADE</p>
        <p style="margin-top:12px;font-style:italic;color:var(--color-text-muted);">&ldquo;Earasers deliver crystal clear sound while keeping my ears safe.&rdquo; — Joey Daniel</p>
      </div>
      <div class="product-content__intro-img" data-reveal data-delay="1">
        <img src="https://www.earasers.shop/cdn/shop/files/WADE_earasers.webp" alt="DJ wearing Earasers" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;border-radius:var(--radius-md);">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

